Events.RelatedDescription: Opened pull request "initial build and test pipeline using actions" (#1478) at dotnet/Open-XML-SDK

Events.RelatedBody:
**Describe the bug**

> Error CS0246 : The type or namespace name 'PartTypeInfo' could not be found (are you missing a using directive or an assembly reference?)

Please release `DocumentFormat.OpenXml.Framework 3.0.0-beta0002` on Nuget


**To Reproduce**

`PartTypeInfo` was moved to the Framework library here https://github.com/dotnet/Open-XML-SDK/commit/a05cb788c2d75d81886e1a1d54e3fddc9d686068 but Framework beta2 is not released

Without the Framework library, ` DocumentFormat.OpenXml 3.0.0-beta0002` is not really usable.
